# Operating system
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# IDE / editor
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Temporary / backup
*.bak
*.tmp
*~

# ModernNetwork runtime artifacts
ModernNetwork/stunnel.conf
ModernNetwork/stunnel.pid

# Design specs / development docs.
# `docs/` excludes the whole tree; `docs/superpower*` is preserved for
# backwards-compat with any files already tracked under that prefix.
docs/
docs/superpower*

# Runtime data: conversation history (generated by Server/history.php)
HISTORY/

# Runtime data: login audit log (appended by Server/auth.php)
LOGIN.txt

# User configuration containing credentials and secrets.
# CONF.ini is shipped as a tracked template with `YOUR_*_HERE` placeholders,
# but once a user fills in real API keys and the [auth] password the file
# should not be re-committed.
CONF.ini